						<summary>

						<p>Slab lying near a well in survey no. 494.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1692, Vikṛiti, Māgha śu. 15, Monday,</hi> corresponding to 1771 A.D., January 30.</p>						

						<p>It seems to refer to the some gift by Tāti-reḍḍi, son of Koppōli Chinnapa-reḍḍi, and Nārāyaṇappa, the <hi rend="italic">karaṇam</hi> of Vellaṭūru.</p>						

						</summary>
